Kipp Hamilton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kipp_Hamilton 0 Kipp Hamilton (August 16, 1934 – January 29, 1981) was an American actress, singer and model. She was the younger sister of producer Joe Hamilton and the sister-in-law of Carol Burnett. Kipp_Hamilton ( August_16_,_1934 – January_29 , 1981 ) was an_American_actress , singer_and_model .
